== 历史 ==
[[File:Grand_Rapids,_Michigan_1955_Yellow_Book.jpg|right]]

296号州际公路/131号美国国道一线的高速公路发展计划是在20世纪50年代诞生。1955年“国家州际公路网通用选址”之后发展成[[州際公路系統|州際公路系統]]，其中就提议在大急流城内及周边修建高速公路，包括市中心附近南北走向的高速公路<ref name="YBGR">{{cite map | title = General Location of National System of Interstate Highways Including All Additional Routes at Urban Areas Designated in September 1955 | map = Grand Rapids | page = 43 | scale = Scale not given | author = Bureau of Public Roads | location = Washington, DC | publisher = [[美国政府出版局|Government Printing Office]] | date = 1955-09 |oclc = 4165975}}</ref>。296号州际公路于1957年加入州际公路网，由[[美国联邦政府|联邦政府]]出资建造<ref name="FHWA">{{cite web | first = Kevin | last = Adderly | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200801230526/https://www.fhwa.dot.gov/planning/national_highway_system/interstate_highway_system/routefinder/table02.cfm | date = 2017-05-23 | title = Table 2: Auxiliary Routes of the Dwight D. Eisenhower National System of Interstate and Defense Highways as of December 31, 2013 | access-date = 2020-10-02 | url = https://www.fhwa.dot.gov/planning/national_highway_system/interstate_highway_system/routefinder/table02.cfm | work = Route Log and Finder List | publisher = Federal Highway Administration | archivedate = 2020-08-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>{{#tag:ref|296号州际公路是在1978年前建成并纳入州际公路网。1978年《地面交通援助法》规定，此前所有其他法案授权建造的州际公路均由联邦政府提供资金，但根据{{usc|23|103(c)(4)(A)}}授权增加的路段例外。<ref>{{cite conference | author = United States Congress | authorlink = 美国国会 | year = 1978 | title = Surface Transportation Assistance Act of 1978 | id = {{USPL|99|599}}}}</ref><ref name="FHWA2">{{cite web | first = Kevin | last = Adderly | date = 2014-01-15 | url = https://www.fhwa.dot.gov/planning/national_highway_system/interstate_highway_system/routefinder/index.cfm | work = Route Log and Finder List | title = Expansion of Mileage | publisher = Federal Highway Administration | access-date = 2020-10-02 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200801234526/https://www.fhwa.dot.gov/planning/national_highway_system/interstate_highway_system/routefinder/index.cfm | archive-date = 2020-08-01}}</ref>|group="注"}}。

1962年12月17日上午十点，位于珍珠街（{{lang|en|Pearl Street}}）和当时196号州际公路/[[16号美国国道|16号美国国道]]之间的131号美国国道正式通车，这段高速公路与296号州际公路完全重叠，与大急流城北面的196号州际公路和市中心（南面）的96号州际公路相连<ref name="296opening" />。之后大急流城西城的96号州际公路和196号州际公路编号对换，即过去的96号如今称196号；过去的196号现名96号<ref name="numbers">{{cite news | newspaper = The Holland Evening Sentinel | title = New Numbers Seen for Road | page = 4 | date = 1963-10-23 | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | issn = 1050-4044 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2018-07-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180712094847/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/10217809/new_numbers_seen_for_road/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/10217809/new-numbers-seen-for-road/ | access-date = 2020-10-02 | via = Newspapers.com | oclc = 13440201 }}</ref>。1969年，大急流城的37号州道改道，以充分利用城市东北部的96号州际公路，不再直连296号州际公路/131号美国国道<ref name="MDSH69GR">{{cite map | author = Michigan Department of State Highways | title = Michigan, Great Lake State: Official Highway Map | year = 1969 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191018021323/https://michiganology.org/uncategorized/digitalFile_77fa9953-5d31-4a07-9bc0-1f64b907999d/ | archivedate = 2019-10-18 | deadurl = no | last-author-amp = yes | author2 = H.M. Gousha | url = https://michiganology.org/uncategorized/digitalFile_77fa9953-5d31-4a07-9bc0-1f64b907999d/ | location = Lansing | publisher = Michigan Department of State Highways | scale = {{#ifeq:{{{inset|}}} | Detroit | c. 1:158,400 | {{#if: {{{inset|}}} | c. 1:190,080 | c. 1:918,720 }}}} | inset = Grand Rapids | oclc = 12701120 | access-date = 2020-10-02 | via = Michigan History Center}}</ref><ref name="MDSH70GR">{{cite map | author = Michigan Department of State Highways | title = Michigan, Great Lake State: Official Highway Map | year = 1970 | location = Lansing | publisher = Michigan Department of State Highways | scale = {{#ifeq:{{{inset|}}} | Detroit | c. 1:158,400 | {{#if: {{{inset|}}} | c. 1:190,080 | c. 1:918,720 }}}} | inset = Grand Rapids |oclc = 12701120}}</ref>。

20世纪70年代末，密歇根州交通部参与联邦公路管理局支持的“积极指导示范项目”（{{lang|en|Positive Guidance Demonstration Project}}），两机构合作审查96号州际公路/37号州道与296号州道/131号国道交汇口附近的路标，密歇根州交通部认定，296号州际公路的标牌有可能误导司机并引发混乱<ref name="memo">{{cite letter | last = Conner | first = Robert E. | recipient = Donald E. Trull | date = 1979-04-11 | title = Removing I-296 Signs in Grand Rapids | location = Washington, DC | publisher = Federal Highway Administration}}</ref>。1979年4月，联邦公路管理局认可州交通部的看法，同意移除所有296号州际公路的路标及公共地图指引<ref name="memo" />。州交通部再于1979年6月22日向[[美国州级公路和运输官员协会|美国州级公路和运输官员协会]]申请落实上述建议，称“除名义上是州际公路外，296号州际公路没有任何用处”<ref>{{cite letter | last = Woodford | first = John P. | recipient = Henrik E. Stafseth | date = 1979-06-22 | title = Request for Official AASHTO Approval to Remove I-296 Route Designation from All References While Retaining the Route as Part of the Interstate System | location = Lansing | publisher = Michigan Department of Transportation}}</ref>，协会于10月13日批准<ref name="AASHTO79">{{cite report | author = Special Committee on U.S. Route Numbering | date = 1979-10-13 | title = Route Numbering Committee Agenda Showing Action Taken by the Executive Committee | type = Report |location = Washington, DC |publisher = American Association of State Highway and Transportation Officials | page = 1}}</ref>。同年10月24日，密歇根州交通部又向联邦公路管理局申请移除路标和地图指令的正式许可，联邦公路管理局于12月3日批准，但要求交通部在正式文献中继续保持296号州际公路的记录，还将公路明确保留在州际公路网中，用于拨款及其他用途<ref name="letter" />。从1980年开始，密歇根州官方地图不再包含296号州际公路的信息<ref name="MDSHT79GR">{{cite map | author = Michigan Department of State Highways and Transportation | title = Michigan, Great Lake State: Official Transportation Map | year = 1979 | edition = 1978–1979 | access-date = 2020-10-02 | via = Michigan History Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191018021331/https://michiganology.org/uncategorized/digitalFile_46a816c0-736d-4ec4-b7a1-f1fef224ee1a/ | location = Lansing | publisher = Michigan Department of State Highways and Transportation | url = https://michiganology.org/uncategorized/digitalFile_46a816c0-736d-4ec4-b7a1-f1fef224ee1a/ | deadurl = no | scale = {{#ifeq:{{{inset|}}} | Detroit | c. 1:158,400 | {{#if: {{{inset|}}} | c. 1:190,080 | c. 1:918,720 }}}} | inset = Grand Rapids | oclc = 12701177 | archivedate = 2019-10-18}}</ref><ref name="MDOT80GR">{{cite map | author = Michigan Department of Transportation | title = Michigan, Great Lake State: Official Transportation Map | year = 1980 | edition = 1980–1981 | scale = {{#ifeq:{{{inset|}}} | Detroit | c. 1:158,400 | {{#if: {{{inset|}}} | c. 1:190,080 | c. 1:918,720 }}}} | location = Lansing | publisher = Michigan Department of Transportation | inset = Grand Rapids | id = {{OCLC|12701177|606211521}}}}</ref>。其他地图偶有标识，如肯特县道路委员会出版的版本<ref name=KCRC08>{{cite map | author = Kent County Road Commission | author2 = REGIS Agency | last-author-amp = yes | year = 2008 | title = Official Road Map | location = Grand Rapids, Michigan | publisher = Kent County Road Commission | scale = 1:95,040 | at = T7N R12W S12 | oclc = 277273068}}</ref>，联邦公路管理局的“路线日志和查找器列表”所列州际公路网也包含296号州际公路<ref name="FHWA" />。
